flowchart TD
    dialog[TrustDialog 弹出] --> choice{用户选择}
    choice -->|Yes, trust| is_home{是否家目录?}
    choice -->|No, exit| shutdown[退出进程]

    is_home -->|是| session_mem[setSessionTrustAccepted\n会话内存，重启失效]
    is_home -->|否| config_file[saveCurrentProjectConfig\n写入 ~/.claude.json]

    session_mem --> continue[继续加载工作区]
    config_file --> continue
    config_file --> inherit[子目录自动继承]
